title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 21 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 21 2022
description:
Dr. Nicole Saphier, NYC practicing physician, Fox News contributor, and author of "Panic Attack: Playing Politics with Science in the Fight Against Covid-19" and "Make America Healthy Again," joins Clay and Buck with covid and mask mandate updates. She says, "If we spend every day avoiding risk, we are risking not living our lives. Life is not about getting to zero risk." Mouse Slap! DeSantis shows the GOP: Don't listen to the opinions of people who will hate you anyway. Nationwide, parents are angry and rejecting the left's radical agenda.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
